{"type": "article", "id": 34091, "title": "没那么多中国人买奢侈品了，以及，KITH 的秋冬新作还不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-04T03:16:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2559, "name": "花瓶"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 34608, "name": "奢侈品报告"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 5622, "name": "Fossil"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 34609, "name": "Sobec"}, {"id": 34610, "name": "David Umemoto"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161104075459maobtJWzgk8TCsel.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/fossil-reinventing-wearables-smart-watch-restructuring-10698888/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Fossil 斥资 1.5 亿美元进行重组，着力发展可穿戴设备</b></a> | 全球最大的时尚腕表生产商之一 Fossil 计划斥资 1.5 亿美元在 2017 －2018 年进行公司业务重组，将重新调整公司的业务分配，集中精力发展可穿戴设备和其他的技术领域。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-11-03/hermes-third-quarter-sales-beat-estimates-on-chinese-growth\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>爱马仕销售额大涨 8.8%</b></a> | 据 bloomberg 消息称，爱马仕的全球市场销售额增长了 8.8%，至 14 亿美元，其中，亚太地区销售额上涨了 14%，实现了两年来的最快增长。受爱马仕 Constance 和 Halzan 包的推动，爱马仕的皮具部门上涨了 16%，丝巾部门尽管受到来自 LVMH 和开云的竞争压力，其销售额也好于预期。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://jingdaily.com/bain-chinese-shoppers-share-of-global-luxury-purchases-drops-to-30/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>2016 年，中国消费者对全球奢侈品市场的贡献下降至 30%</b></a> | 贝恩咨询的奢侈品年度报告 Bain Luxury Study 报告指出，在 2016 年，中国消费者购买奢侈品的数量在去年的基础上再度下滑，对全球奢侈品市场的贡献下降至 30%。贝恩曾在 2015 年的报告中指出，由于海外购买奢侈品的数量增加，中国的本土奢侈品市场下降了 2%。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">法国新晋街头品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/sobec-2016-fw-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Sobec 发布了全新的 2016 秋冬系列</a>。这个以不同品牌的“拼接”款 T-shirt 而成名的品牌，本季选用了校园运动服饰作为拼接的主题。该系列已于官网全面上架，定价 69 美元起。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104074932Y6WQAJfdTy8GUVN5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104074934Am9gkJ2Ojb1YpQq8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104074934pCxqa0zPrDgt3lUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104074935GIf0ZDHaFMe86ySi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104074941cmKQ23saMhOovRFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075051TpXnJENKwaY0hlsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>抢不到 KENZO x H&amp;M 合作款的话，可以下载一个<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/gadgets/hm-x-kenzo-emojis-so-you-can-celebrate-the-collection/#\" rel=\"nofollow\"> KENZO x H&amp;M 专属 emoji </a>来玩。为了庆祝其合作款的开售，KENZO x H&amp;M 推出了适用于 iPhone 和 Android 的表情，搜索 EMOTIKENZO 即可下载。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075122EB2cnSJDOTXIAFVh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p>野兽派雕塑家 David Umemoto 以法国高端帽子品牌 Larose Paris 为灵感，打造了一组<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/larose-paris-x-david-umemoto-vase-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">混凝土花瓶</a>。这组花瓶最大的亮点在于它可以被拆卸成 15 块，进行随意组合。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075133gwrtGs5j6qHRch4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075148J5SyAIBZ7Xt2wabY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075155GrPhO1vcREnmlF7U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666921\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104075203PviVaxu1LnB0cqht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>庆祝“Off the Wall” 50 周年，Vans 最经典的<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/03/vans-50th-anniversary-pro-classics-collection-fw16/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Full Cab </a>又回归了。在 1989 年，Vans 为旗下签约滑手 Steve Caballero 推出了其首款签名鞋 Full Cab，比起如今的 Half Cab，它在脚踝防护方面要更出色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611040833136kRA4CcBtznblV3J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611040833212Tupc9IZmzvMVWGL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104083321WKL3iXSkZ2MHtfNo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104083321pemf0QKwFdMBxRzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104083327z6uYOLElebPp9dmA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>美国潮店 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/kith-x-iro-collaboration-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH 与法国奢侈品牌 Iro 首度合作</a>，推出 2016 秋冬男女装系列，这个系列以大地色系为主色调，经破坏处理的连帽衫和运动裤，以及羊羔毛内里的外套成为亮点。该系列将于美国东部时间 11 月 4 日正式登陆 KITH 各大门店。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101319YgVXNEpc6F7Gr4um.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101331QsjxcT8ymZduND3B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101331evZyhr1J8VCMbkLf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110410133187U5OulaoAM64YEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101331uRxClHcEDWb3X2rB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101331GaCsShl3enjwtbUL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110410133260arPpfEDqehTj8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101332ynpZT1i2Sw6Oame4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101332LuZMpz8enTCidrKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101332kicZRVlYH70nC3a9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104101332U4dbm6JYMxoKSCyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161104111619YSOVCEA2wo6p3ktI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}